# /etc/cron.d/ats-auto-login
# Daily Zerodha auto-login. Drops to /etc/cron.d/ via the install script.
#
# Schedule: 00:40 UTC = 06:10 IST, Mon-Fri (Indian markets are closed weekends).
# Tier 13: moved earlier so the access-token refresh happens close to the daily
# ~06:00 IST Kite token expiry instead of 2h 50m AFTER it. Eliminates the morning
# "token expired" window users were seeing on /api/profile.
# The script itself adds 0-60